â£
I have always been a firm believer that everything happens for a reason. Whether it is something positive or negative. I think that all stems from our mindset. 
â£
One thing I have learned over the last year of being a coach is how focusing on my own personal development is so important. I now read a chapter of a personal development book every morning and it has been a game changer. 
â£
Positive actions repeated daily will lead to positive outcomes. Having a positive outlook on LIFE will lead to a more positive life. 
â£
Whereas being negative, constantly looking at the glass as half empty, and finding something wrong in every situation is going to lead to negative outcomes and a negative, miserable life. 
â£
